{"word":"πενθέω","slug":"πενθέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πενθέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πένθος'><el>πένθος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to bewail, lament, mourn for</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>πενθεῖν τινὰ ὡς τεθνεῶτα</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be mourned for</i>, <b><a href='S:Isocrates'>Isocr.</a></b> <p/>"}]}